org.opendaylight.yang.gen.v1.urn.opendaylight.packet.ipv6.rev140528.ipv6.packet.received.packet.chain.packet

Interface Ipv6Packet

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.Augmentable<Ipv6Packet>, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataContainer, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataObject, Ipv6PacketFields, Packet, PacketFields

    public interface Ipv6Packet
extends org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataObject, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.Augmentable<Ipv6Packet>, Ipv6PacketFields, Packet

    This class represents the following YANG schema fragment defined in module ipv6-packet 

     case ipv6-packet {
     leaf version {
         type uint8;
     }
     leaf dscp {
         type dscp;
     }
     leaf ecn {
         type uint8;
     }
     leaf flow-label {
         type uint32;
     }
     leaf ipv6-length {
         type uint16;
     }
     leaf next-header {
         type known-ip-protocols;
     }
     leaf hop-limit {
         type uint8;
     }
     leaf source-ipv6 {
         type ipv6-address;
     }
     leaf destination-ipv6 {
         type ipv6-address;
     }
     list extension-headers {
         key     leaf next-header {
             type known-ip-protocols;
         }
         leaf length {
             type uint16;
         }
         leaf data {
             type binary;
         }
     }
     leaf payload-offset {
         type int32;
     }
     leaf payload-length {
         type int32;
     }
 }
    The schema path to identify an instance is ipv6-packet/ipv6-packet-received/packet-chain/packet/ipv6-packet
